1. Generate ecloud.war
2. Remove other apps deployed on your tomcat host
3. Create 'emscloud' database.
4. Change /var/lib/tomcat6/conf/context.xml to introduce new resource for 'emscloud' database.
5. deploy ecloud.war to your tomcat and restart the server. Schema should be generated automatically on emscloud.
6. You might have to insert one user record for admin/admin login. Checkout ecloud/artifacts/sql/InstallSQL.sql.